59	// notesFileSuffix that we want to treat special. It goes through the templating engine
60	// but it's not a yaml file (resource) hence can't have hooks, etc. And the user actually
61	// wants to see this file after rendering in the status command. However, it must be a suffix
62	// since there can be filepath in front of it.
